            <div type="translation">
                <p xml:lang="en">
                    <persName corresp="#felix" xml:lang="la">Flavius Felix</persName>, for himself and for his wife 
                    <persName corresp="#lucia" xml:lang="la">Lucia</persName>, had this made during their lifetime at their own expense. 
                    So that no one, after their death, may be buried in this tomb, a fine of two pounds of gold shall be paid to the treasury.
                </p>
                <p xml:lang="it">
                    <persName corresp="#felix" xml:lang="la">Flavius Felix</persName>, per sé e per la moglie <persName corresp="#lucia" xml:lang="la">Lucia</persName>, fece realizzare quest’arca da vivo, a proprie spese.  
                    Affinché nessuno, dopo la loro morte, venga deposto in questa sepoltura, è prevista una multa di due libbre d’oro a favore del fisco.
                </p>
            </div>
